      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is an ideal choice for a buyer looking for a dependable daily driver without the premium price of a showroom-ready car. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery shows signs of regular use, including some staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly maintained, though it may soon require routine service for wear items like brake pads. It\u2019s a solid, functional vehicle that prioritizes performance over perfect aesthetics.",
