    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles high-torque loads without fatigue. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and precise MacPherson strut/multi-link geometry. While the finish shows minor road wear, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a pure, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
